{"tid":191364,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"籃球是世界最受歡迎運動","createTime":"2017-04-07T21:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T05:28:50.000Z","uid":98942,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28526d3af0fc6f2fdfa66aeaa7779298f729a658","tid":191364,"uid":98942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T21:45:23.000Z","msg":"點解籃球甘受歡迎同好玩但個d咩國際賽矛乜人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而咩垃圾足球既世界盃甘多人睇 見到刀想嘔<br />\n籃球明明戰術又多過足球<br />\n籃球d球員又高大令仔過足球果d死矮撚<br />\n點解我話籃球受歡迎過足球？<br />\n你地睇下平時小學中學果到既小息午膳全部刀系打籃球 足球撚去左邊<br />\n囡囡又中意睇d高大令仔打波 小妹有時刀按捺不住<br />\n玩開籃球既手足你地話系吾系<br />\n死足撚仲要講到足球好勁<br />\n歡迎玩籃球既手足一齊推廣 趕走足球撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：下年升中一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d4983c97f8c4db3996dd8ab03a5a9bf38a0909","tid":191364,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T22:30:10.000Z","msg":"呢度無人識你喎"},{"pid":"9ff8d7107ce08c1019b2e365f8f9ca2f9f61e072","tid":191364,"uid":98942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T22:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度無人識你喎</blockquote><br />\nChing吾洗識我 有心搞好籃球就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57011977f010131206a87669ec32e55085f824d0","tid":191364,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T22:51:11.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 玩具都話系運動😂"},{"pid":"2326a8bc8a33dc3f8632ff6785583dac7b203d4e","tid":191364,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T00:15:26.000Z","msg":"曲ching上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847e0fbc40952db7966ec42f7fa0a3a819e5117c","tid":191364,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}